descriptionHtml:
Thanks to the mein real app, don't miss out on any promotions, offers and themes at the mein real store of your choice. With the app, you have the opportunity to view the offers in the current brochure. You can also use the store search to easily find out about current opening hours, contact options, and local services. The route planner helps you reach the mein real store of your choice even more easily.

We've made the app even fresher and more intuitive for you by switching to mein real. The app makes it very easy for you to get in touch with us - you can reach us quickly by e-mail or phone under the Customer Service menu item.

Last but not least, the app provides you with many PAYBACK services related to your loyalty points and coupons. For example, you can view your PAYBACK points balance, use eCoupons and digital shopping vouchers.

The advantages of the app in a nutshell:
- Current promotions, offers and topics on the homepage at all times
- Overview of offers and brochures with a few clicks and swipes
- Information about the mein real store of your choice at a glance
- Route planner and practical shopping list
- PAYBACK services such as eCoupons, digital shopping vouchers and viewing your points balance
